snippet.title: Eversoul | G-Star PV 2022 [ENG version]
snippet.description:
👇Follow us for the latest news, Events and more Soul Teasers!👇
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Eversoul_EN

We hope you got a good glimpse of Eversoul during G-Star 2022 event!
Take a look at the latest trailer presented at the most important game show of the year in Korea!

Get ready. She is going to summon you, and your life won't be the same anymore...

Don't forget to subscribe and follow us on Twitter @Eversou_EN, so you won't miss the pre-registration phase on November 29th and the upcoming announcements!

#Eversoul #kakaogames
